  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Global challenges (not only) for journalists</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">Glob&#xE1;lne v&#xFD;zvy (nielen) pre &#x17E;urnalistov</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="SK">&lt;p&gt;Partneri projektu Glob&#xE1;lne v&#xFD;zvy (nielen) pre &#x17E;urnalistov - &#x17E;iadate&#x13E;, Katedra &#x17E;urnalistiky Univerzity Komensk&#xE9;ho (K&#x17D;) a spravodajsk&#xFD; port&#xE1;l HNonile.sk - prich&#xE1;dzaj&#xFA; s unik&#xE1;tnou iniciat&#xED;vou, ktorej cie&#x13E;om je podpori&#x165; budovanie kapac&#xED;t, v&#xFD;menu sk&#xFA;senost&#xED; a medziodborov&#xE9; sie&#x165;ovanie akademikov a odborn&#xED;kov z rozvojovej a medi&#xE1;lnej oblasti. Po&#x10D;as projektu vytvor&#xED;me pracovn&#xFA; skupinu 15 odborn&#xED;kov z r&#xF4;znych oblast&#xED; rozvoja a m&#xE9;di&#xED;, ktor&#xED; pod veden&#xED;m metodika s expert&#xED;zou v rozvojovom vzdel&#xE1;van&#xED; vytvoria skript&#xE1; a kurikulum celofakultn&#xE9;ho predmetu Glob&#xE1;lne v&#xFD;zvy (nielen) pre &#x17E;urnalistov. Predmet n&#xE1;sledne v troch semestroch zrealizuj&#xFA; na K&#x17D;, bude v&#x161;ak otvoren&#xFD; z&#xE1;ujemcom zo v&#x161;etk&#xFD;ch pracov&#xED;sk Univerzity Komensk&#xE9;ho.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&lt;p&gt;Partners of the project Global Challenges (not only) for journalists - the applicant, Department of Journalism at Comenius University and&#xA0;the economical news portal HNonline.sk - come with a unique initiative, which aims to support capacity building, exchange of experience and interdisciplinary networking of academics and experts from development and media area. During the project, create a working group of 15 experts from various areas of development and media, who lead methodology with expertise in developing training curriculum and create scripts faculty courses Global Challenges (not only) for journalists.&lt;/p&gt;</narrative>
  </description>
